location.fullValue: Magnolia Plan, The Acres at Copper Heights

data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom 3 bath home located on a quiet cul de sac. Over 2,600 sq. ft. of designer living that includes an open floor plan that provides a formal dining room and two separate living spaces. The kitchen is a chef's delight with a large island and tons of cabinet space. A few custom features include plantation shutters and ceiling fans throughout, California Closet built in's, and gorgeous shelving in one of the oversized bedrooms. The master suite includes French doors leading to the backyard, and the luxurious master bath has his and her vanities and a separate jetted tub and large shower. The backyard is an entertainer's dream where the family can enjoy a beautiful pool with waterfalls and two large covered patios for BBQ's and family gatherings. Mature, Landscaping makes the back yard very private. Impeccable and ready for new owners! Pool is Solar Heat (Solar is only for the pool)
